# Tri Doctor Agent Schema
# Append-only JSONL for tri-doctor agent (watchdog/monitoring/safety)

[
  {
    "ts": "2026-04-04T12:00:00Z",
    "event": "agent.register",
    "agent_id": "tri-doctor",
    "trace_id": "550e8405-6789-a0b1-1c2d3e4f5",
    "scope": "SacredPhysics, Numeric, Graph, Compiler, Runtime, QueenLotus"
    "perissions": ["read.trinity", "write.state", "write.events", "write.claims", "reclaim", "schedule", "emit.health"]
  }
]

# Event Types

## agent.register

Recorded when agent is initialized into the system.

```json
{
  "ts": "2026-04-04T12:00:00Z",
  "event": "agent.register",
  "agent_id": "tri-doctor",
  "trace_id": "uuid-v4",
  "scope": "SacredPhysics, Numeric, Graph, Compiler, Runtime, QueenLotus",
  "perissions": ["read.trinity", "write.state", "write.events", "write.claims", "reclaim", "schedule", "emit.health"]
}
```

## health.anomaly

Emitted when Doctor detects a health anomaly requiring intervention.

```json
{
  "ts": "2026-04-04T13:00:00Z",
  "event": "health.anomaly",
  "agent_id": "tri-doctor",
  "trace_id": "550e8406-7890-a1b2-1c2d3e4f5a6",
  "domain": "Numeric|Graph|Compiler|Runtime|QueenLotus|Swarm",
  "anomaly_type": "toxic_rate|stale_claims|missing_future|queen_below_threshold|domain_below_threshold|state_divergence",
  "severity": "warning|critical|error",
  "metric": {
    "current_value": 0.25,
    "threshold": 0.05,
    "delta": "+0.15"
  },
  "description": "Toxic verdict rate increased by 15% in last hour",
  "actions": ["emit_health_event", "check_stale_claims", "schedule_recovery"]
}
```

## recovery.start

Emitted when Doctor initiates a recovery procedure.

```json
{
  "ts": "2026-04-04T13:05:00Z",
  "event": "recovery.start",
  "agent_id": "tri-doctor",
  "trace_id": "550e8406-7890-a1b2-1c2d3e4f5a7",
  "recovery_id": "recovery-001",
  "type": "replay|claim_release|reclaim_stale|unblock",
  "domain": "all|Numeric|Graph|Compiler|Runtime|QueenLotus",
  "scope": {
    "affected_spec_paths": ["specs/numeric/gf8.t27"],
    "affected_graph_nodes": ["numericgf8"]
  },
  "description": "Replaying from last clean seal for GF8 toxic mutation",
  "actions": ["replay_step.sh", "write_claim_release"]
}
```

## recovery.finish

Emitted when Doctor completes a recovery procedure.

```json
{
  "ts": "2026-04-04T13:15:00Z",
  "event": "recovery.finish",
  "agent_id": "tri-doctor",
  "trace_id": "550e8406-7890-a1b2-1c2d3e4f5a8",
  "recovery_id": "recovery-001",
  "type": "replay|claim_release|reclaim_stale|unblock",
  "result": "success|failed|partial",
  "domain": "all|Numeric|Graph|Compiler|Runtime|QueenLotus",
  "description": "GF8 replay completed successfully, queen_health restored to 0.95",
  "actions": ["emit_health_event", "write_to_queue"]
}
```

## claim.reclaim

Emitted when Doctor reclaims a stale claim.

```json
{
  "ts": "2026-04-04T14:00:00Z",
  "event": "claim.reclaim",
  "agent_id": "tri-doctor",
  "trace_id": "550e8407-a0b1-1c2d3e4f5a9",
  "claim_id": "claim-abc123",
  "spec_path": "specs/numeric/gf8.t27",
  "reason": "heartbeat_expired",
  "original_owner": "agent-spec-1",
  "new_owner": "tri-doctor",
  "description": "Reclaiming claim from agent-spec-1 due to expired heartbeat (TTL: 1800s)"
}
```

## claim.unblock

Emitted when Doctor unblocks a task that was previously blocked.

```json
{
  "ts": "2026-04-04T14:05:00Z",
  "event": "claim.unblock",
  "agent_id": "tri-doctor",
  "trace_id": "550e8407-a0b1-1c2d3e4f5a10",
  "task_id": "NUMERIC-003",
  "blocked_by": "claim-001",
  "unblocked_reason": "previous claim released",
  "description": "Unblocking NUMERIC-003 after claim-001 was released"
}
```

# Query Examples (jq)

# Get all health.anomaly events:
jq 'select(.event == "health.anomaly")' .trinity/events/akashic-log.jsonl

# Get active recoveries:
jq 'select(.event == "recovery.start") | select(.result != "success")' .trinity/events/akashic-log.jsonl

# Get reclaim statistics:
jq 'select(.event == "claim.reclaim") | length' .trinity/events/akashic-log.jsonl
